{
  "stem": "1473.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And you can stay Jewish, it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I [? don't-- ?] there, I had a complete collapse.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- I came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was so confusing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And intellectually, I said, I'm going to find my father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm going to find him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somehow I must have known I wouldn't.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then you know, in Switzerland they have the habit of what they call a [FRENCH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They give you-- they drug you, 24 hours a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then, kind of, when you wake up, you kind of forgot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that evidently happened.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because my attendance sheet showed that I had an unexplained absence of two weeks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I went back to Switzerland with my husband, and I was married and I went to this doctor, and I asked, what-- what did you treat me for here?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What did you?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he just patted you on the back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, oh, well, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had a very bad this or that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you just don't remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It wasn't that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Eventually the sister of [FRENCH] Rose told me that that's-- that's indeed what they did.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So [CRYING] I woke up from that and went back to school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this, of course, now was 1945.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So news came from America and all that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I wanted not to come to America.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was so angry at the relatives here-- at those American relatives.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I wanted to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was not eligible, because I had somewhere to go.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So the OSE told me that I was just ineligible to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I could either stay in Switzerland or go.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
